<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Cotización #{{orderId}}</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --primary-soft: #eff4ff;
            --text-main: #111827;
            --text-muted: #6b7280;
            --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
            --bg: #f9fafb;
            --danger: #b91c1c;
            --radius: 8px;
            --font-main: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            background: #f9fafb;
            color: #111827;
            padding: 32px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .quote {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .quote__header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 24px;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .quote__company {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            flex: 2;
        }

        .quote__logo {
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #eff4ff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .quote__logo img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .quote__company-info h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .quote__company-info p {
            margin: 2px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .quote__meta {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .quote__meta h2 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .quote__meta .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .quote__to {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 32px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .quote__to h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .quote__to p {
            margin: 2px 0;
        }

        .quote__items table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .quote__items thead {
            background: #eff4ff;
        }

        .quote__items th,
        .quote__items td {
            padding: 10px 8px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .quote__items th {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .quote__totals {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .quote__notes {
            flex: 2;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .quote__notes h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .quote__amounts {
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background: #fefefe;
        }

        .amount-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .amount-row--total {
            margin-top: 8px;
            padding-top: 8px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #e5e7eb;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .quote__footer {
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding-top: 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .quote__signature {
            text-align: right;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="quote">
        <header class="quote__header">
            <div class="quote__company">
                <div class="quote__logo">
                    <img src="{{logo}}" alt="Logo" />
                </div>
                <div class="quote__company-info">
                    <h1>CE02</h1>
                    <p>Cerro de las palomas 115-A, Dr. Jorge Jimenez Cantú, Tlalnepantla de Baz, México.</p>
                    <p>Tel: +52 55 2730 4665 · irueda@ceo2.com</p>
                    <p>Sitio web: www.ceo2.mx</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="quote__meta">
                <h2>COTIZACIÓN</h2>
                <p><span class="label">Folio:</span> {{orderId}}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Fecha:</span> {{date}}</p>
                <p><span class="label">Válida hasta:</span> {{validUntil}}</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="quote__to">
            <div>
                <h3>Información del Cliente</h3>
                <p><strong>Cliente:</strong> {{customerFullname}}</p>
                <p><strong>Contacto:</strong> {{customerName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Correo:</strong> {{customerEmail}}</p>
                <p><strong>Teléfono:</strong> {{customerPhone}}</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Condiciones generales</h3>
                <p>Forma de pago: Transferencia bancaria</p>
                <p>Tiempo de entrega: 5–7 días hábiles</p>
                <p>Moneda: MXN</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="quote__items">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Concepto</th>
                        <th>Cantidad</th>
                        <th>Precio unitario</th>
                        <th>Descuento</th>
                        <th>Importe</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each items}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{name}}</td>
                        <td>{{quantity}}</td>
                        <td>{{unitPriceFormatted}}</td>
                        <td>0%</td>
                        <td>{{lineTotalFormatted}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>

        <section class="quote__totals">
            <div class="quote__notes">
                <h3>Notas</h3>
                <p>
                    • Los precios incluyen IVA.<br />
                    • La cotización puede modificarse en caso de cambios en el alcance.<br />
                    • Para iniciar el proyecto se requiere un anticipo del 50%.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="quote__amounts">
                <div class="amount-row">
                    <span>Subtotal:</span>
                    <span>{{subtotalFormatted}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="amount-row">
                    <span>IVA (16%):</span>
                    <span>{{taxFormatted}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="amount-row amount-row--total">
                    <span>Total:</span>
                    <span>{{totalFormatted}} MXN</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="quote__footer">
            <div>
                <p><strong>Cuenta bancaria:</strong></p>
                <p>Banco Ejemplo · CLABE: 000 000 0000 000000 · Beneficiario: Nombre de la Empresa</p>
            </div>
            <div class="quote__signature">
                <p>______________________________</p>
                <p><strong>Nombre del responsable</strong></p>
                <p>Puesto / Área</p>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>